data.description: Here is a lovely Victorian style home on 13.13 acres of land nestled among old pines and large sugar maples.  The house is situated on a high piece of land with views of Gower Brook.  This home offers 3 bedrooms, with primary on main level, 2 .5 bathrooms and a lower level kitchen set up, 2 sunrooms, a jacuzzi, hardwood floors and open living space and so much more. Primary bedroom opens into a sunroom, offers walk-in closets, solid doors, attached two car garage. Walk-out basement with large play room and a kitchen offers many possibilities. This contemporary Victorian has modern charm.  There is a separate garage and workshop area all ready for your needs and big enough to store a motorhome.
